history.content:
@1193 says there are seats being set aside for you (EECS sophomores through seniors), which is why we are saying it's okay to Phase I. Not all EECS sophomores through seniors will want to wait, however and some are choosing to use Phase II. As far as I know, the class will not decrease from 350 seats. 

Also keep in mind that we are setting aside seats for LSCS sophomores through seniors, however they may not choose to take 16B since it is not required. Any of those unused seats will also open on Aug 16.

Hope this helps!
